title: Prachinburi Provincial Administrative Organization Stadium
text: Prachinburi Provincial Administrative Organization Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Prachinburi%20province">Prachinburi province</a>, <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Prachinburi%20United%20F.C.">Prachinburi United F.C.</a>. The stadium holds 3,000 people.
